OL,3,CHospital radio volunteer jailed for
OL,4,C5,000 indecent images of children
OL,6,FA hospital radio volunteer in Guernsey
OL,7,Fhas been sentenced to 20 months in
OL,8,Fprison after police found more than
OL,9,F5,000 indecent images of children on
OL,10,Fdevices in his home.
OL,12,FSimon Gallienne - who volunteered at
OL,13,FJubilee Hospital Radio - was arrested
OL,14,Fon 31 October 2024 after material was
OL,15,Ffound on two hard drives and a laptop
OL,16,Fseized during a police search.
OL,18,FHe was charged with possessing 54 of
OL,19,Fthe most serious Category A images, 58
OL,20,FCategory B images, and 4,967 Category
OL,21,FC images.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
