OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772572328
OL,3,CHospital radio volunteer jailed for
OL,4,C5,000 indecent images of children
OL,6,FOfficers also found tens of thousands
OL,7,Fof "borderline" images, such as
OL,8,Fchildren in gymnastics gear.
OL,10,FAn investigation into Gallienne's
OL,11,Fdevices was stopped because there was
OL,12,Fso much content that it had passed a
OL,13,Fthreshold where Guernsey Police lacked
OL,14,Fthe manpower to continue categorising
OL,15,Fthe data.
OL,17,FGallienne initially denied knowledge
OL,18,Fof the images, arguing he was
OL,19,Fsearching on the dark web for naturist
OL,20,Fphotography, but eventually pleaded
OL,21,Fguilty to all the charges.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772572328
OL,3,CHospital radio volunteer jailed for
OL,4,C5,000 indecent images of children
OL,6,FAt Guernsey's Royal Court, Advocate
OL,7,FSam Steele argued that Gallienne's
OL,8,Fdeterioration in mental health
OL,9,Ftriggered his offending and stated
OL,10,Fthat the defendant's wife had forgiven
OL,11,Fhim - she was in the public gallery
OL,12,Fduring the sentencing.
OL,14,FThe court also heard Gallienne suffers
OL,15,Ffrom a list of physical and mental
OL,16,Failments, including diabetes,
OL,17,Fdepression, and an abdominal hernia,
OL,18,Fwhich was taken into account for his
OL,19,Fsentencing.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772572328
OL,3,CHospital radio volunteer jailed for
OL,4,C5,000 indecent images of children
OL,6,FAdvocate Steele argued that it would
OL,7,Fbe difficult for him in prison.
OL,9,FWhile Gallienne's sentence was reduced
OL,10,Fby a third, he was ultimately given a
OL,11,F20-month prison term, an extended two-
OL,12,Fyear supervision order after release,
OL,13,Fand put on the sex offenders register
OL,14,Ffor five years.
OL,16,FJudge Graeme McKerrell concluded: "For
OL,17,Fevery indecent image of a child, there
OL,18,Fis a child harmed. It is people like
OL,19,Fyou who create demand for these
OL,20,Fimages; it is people like you that
OL,21,Fmean children are harmed."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
